    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190150/extras/048494be14e4d1ee67fb53fb071d3e89.avif?t=1754978183\" width=600 height=184 /></span><strong>The Last Humble Bee</strong> is a heart-buzzing bumble bee rogue-like where you swashbuckle, bounce, and barrel-blast through a desaturated pixel art world to &quot;Save the Bees&quot; from eternal damnation!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Play as a Swashbuckling Warrior Bee:</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190150/extras/ad4e70934472ce915d87cdce1ee58660.poster.avif?t=1754978183\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190150/extras/ad4e70934472ce915d87cdce1ee58660.webm?t=1754978183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190150/extras/ad4e70934472ce915d87cdce1ee58660.mp4?t=1754978183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Jump, dodge/roll, and attack your way to bumble bee glory!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Customize your own Deck of Magical Upgrades:</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190150/extras/aac4426c8630f6519c49bf25f2d4f215.poster.avif?t=1754978183\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190150/extras/aac4426c8630f6519c49bf25f2d4f215.webm?t=1754978183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190150/extras/aac4426c8630f6519c49bf25f2d4f215.mp4?t=1754978183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>A deckbuilding system enables you to choose your own (random) upgrades.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Lose yourself in huge maps, and get the zoomies:</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190150/extras/6c00d49d837f9ce147c199deca6f5730.poster.avif?t=1754978183\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190150/extras/6c00d49d837f9ce147c199deca6f5730.webm?t=1754978183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190150/extras/6c00d49d837f9ce147c199deca6f5730.mp4?t=1754978183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Explore for treasure or jump into a barrel cannon to blast across the map!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Features:</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design, Art, and Audio harken back to the days of 16-bit</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bounce over gaps! Duel with enemies! Find treasure! Uncover secrets! Upgrade!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A light touch to narrative with humor, levity, and heart</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >De-saturated pixel art with big chunky outlines</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging gameplay that warmly welcomes newcomers, yet leaves room for expert-level maneuvering</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Developer’s Note:</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks so much for playing The Last Humble Bee!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I consider this game complete and am now focusing on new projects, but I’m really proud of what we made together. I may revisit Humble Bee down the road, but for now, I’m excited to keep moving forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cheers, Jacob Weersing</p>",
